  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2162",
  "title": "v2 rangeSlider/Rheostat: reinstate handle-lower/upper classes from v1",
  "body": "v1's slider had the following classes:\r\n- `ais-range-slider--handle-lower`\r\n- `ais-range-slider--handle-upper`\r\n\r\nWithout them, it can be annoying to style something like this, and makes migration from v1 to v2 more troublesome:\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2017-05-23 at 8 23 07 am](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/18329/26354235/be2d3c64-3f91-11e7-96ff-c7b728970d06.png)\r\n\r\nWould be great to have them back!\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\nv2.0.0-beta.2",
